{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"datalist","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sumário","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O elemento HTML <em>Datalist</em> (<span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&lt;datalist&gt;</span>) contém um conjunto de elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a> que representam as opções possíveis para o valor de outros controles.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"Contexto de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Conteúdo permitido</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories#phrasing content\">Phrasing content</a> ou qualquer quantidade de elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a> (ou nenhum)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Omissão de tags</td>\n   <td>Nenhuma, ambas as tags inicial e final são obrigatórias</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Elementos pais permitidos</td>\n   <td>Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"en/HTML/Content categories#phrasing content\">phrasing content</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Documento normativo</td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/the-button-element.html#the-datalist-element\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">HTML5, section 4.10.10</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Esse elemento não tem nenhum atributo a não ser os <a href=\"/en-US/HTML/Global_attributes\" title=\"en/HTML/Global attributes\">global attributes</a>, comuns para todos os elementos.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interface_do_dom","title":"Interface do DOM","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Esse elemento implementa a interface <code><a href=\"/en-US/DOM/HTMLDataListElement\" title=\"en/DOM/HTMLDataListElement\">HTMLDataListElement</a></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">list</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>browsers<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>datalist</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>browsers<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Chrome<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Firefox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Internet Explorer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Opera<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>option</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Safari<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>datalist</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://media.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/samples/html/datalist.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">View Live Examples</a></p>\n\n<p>Esse código HTML é renderizado assim no Firefox 4:</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"datalist.png\" class=\"default internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/4982/=datalist.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibilidade","title":"Compatibilidade","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>20</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>9.5</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill","title":"Polyfill","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Inclua este polyfill para fornecer suporte para navegadores mais antigos e atualmente incompatíveis:<br>\n <a href=\"https://github.com/mfranzke/datalist-polyfill\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">datalist-polyfill</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li class=\"last\">O elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, especialmente seu atributo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input#attr-list\"><code>list</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\">O elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"sumário"},{"text":"Contexto de uso","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Interface do DOM","id":"interface_do_dom"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Compatibilidade","id":"compatibilidade"},{"text":"Polyfill","id":"polyfill"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML Datalist (<datalist>) contém um conjunto de elementos <option> que representam as opções possíveis para o valor de outros controles.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<datalist>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<datalist>: The HTML Data List element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"datalist","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<datalist> : l'élément de liste des données","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<datalist>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<datalist>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<datalist>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"datalist","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/datalist","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/datalist/index.html","last_commit_url":"https: